--  GlOBAL FUNCTIONS

function GetSnapPointWorldPosition(params)
--   params = {
--     obj   = Object that snap points are attached to
--     snapPointNum = the snapPoint number
--     addedHeight = any extra height to move to
--   }
  local snapPosition = params.obj.getSnapPoints()[params.snapPointNum].position
  snapPosition.x = params.obj.getScale().x * snapPosition.x + params.obj.getPosition().x
  snapPosition.y = params.obj.getScale().y * snapPosition.y + params.addedHeight + params.obj.getPosition().y
  snapPosition.z = params.obj.getScale().z * snapPosition.z + params.obj.getPosition().z
  return snapPosition
end

function GetSnapPointWorldRotation(params)
  --   params = {
  --     obj   = Object that snap points are attached to
  --     snapPointNum = the snapPoint number
  --   }
  local snapRotation = params.obj.getSnapPoints()[params.snapPointNum].rotation
  snapRotation.x = params.obj.getScale().x * snapRotation.x + params.obj.getRotation().x
  snapRotation.y = params.obj.getScale().y * snapRotation.y + params.obj.getRotation().y
  snapRotation.z = params.obj.getScale().z * snapRotation.z + params.obj.getRotation().z
  return snapRotation
end

ObjectStates.LuaScript:
dice = {}
dice[1] = getObjectFromGUID("ad5c10")
dice[2] = getObjectFromGUID("a33d3a")
dice[3] = getObjectFromGUID("857031")
dice[4] = getObjectFromGUID("37be45")
dice[5] = getObjectFromGUID("671cb6")
diceTray = getObjectFromGUID("f215f3")
auctionPlate = getObjectFromGUID("f3d588")
smallBag = getObjectFromGUID("ce3dae")
medBag = getObjectFromGUID("02ac30")
largeBag = getObjectFromGUID("a225db")
auctionScriptZ = getObjectFromGUID('d7fe55')

function RollDice() -- roll the auction dice
  ClearAuction()
  -- check the amount of players, and roll the corresponding die
  playerCount = Global.getVar("playerCount")
  for i = playerCount,1,-1  do
    dice[i].setPosition({diceTray.getPosition().x + 3 - i,diceTray.getPosition().y + 1,diceTray.getPosition().z})
    dice[i].Roll()
    dice[i].Roll()
  end

  -- setup wait function until the dice stop rolling
  Wait.condition(
    function() -- set up the auction plate
      SetAuction(dice)
    end,
    function() -- Check if the dice are level
      return CheckDice()
    end
  )
end

function CheckDice() -- check the dice state
  for i, die in ipairs(dice) do
    if (die != null) then
      if not (die.resting) then return false end
      end
    end
  return true
end

function SetAuction(dice) -- for each die, update the auction
  for i = playerCount,1,-1  do
    moveMaoiToAuction(dice[i],i)
  end
  firstTurnFlag = false -- remove first round flag
  --EndRound1()
end

function moveMaoiToAuction(inDice,i) -- move maoi from bag to auction plate snap Point
  -- inDice = Dice
  -- snapPoint number

  -- retrieve the postion of the Snap Point
  params = {
    obj   = auctionPlate,
    snapPointNum = i,
    addedHeight = 1
  }
  local placePosition = Global.call("GetSnapPointWorldPosition",params)

  -- Retrieve the rotation of the Snap Point
  params2 = {
    obj          = auctionPlate,
    snapPointNum = i,
  }
  local placeRotation = Global.call("GetSnapPointWorldRotation",params2)

  -- retrieve if this is the first turn
  local firstTurnFlag = getObjectFromGUID("de1bed").getValue() == 1

  -- Dependant of the dice number and if it is the first Turn
  -- Move a Maoi object to the auction plate at the desired location/Rotation
  if (inDice.getRotationValue() == 1 and firstTurnFlag) then
    smallBag.takeObject(
    {
      position          = placePosition,
      rotation          = placeRotation,
      smooth            = true
    })
  end
  if (inDice.getRotationValue() == 2 or inDice.getRotationValue() == 3) then
    smallBag.takeObject(
    {
      position          = placePosition,
     rotation          = placeRotation,
      smooth            = true
    })
  end
  if (inDice.getRotationValue() == 4 or inDice.getRotationValue() == 5) then
    medBag.takeObject(
    {
      position          = placePosition,
      rotation          = placeRotation,
      smooth            = true
    })
  end
  if (inDice.getRotationValue() == 6 and firstTurnFlag) then
    medBag.takeObject(
    {
      position          = placePosition,
      rotation          = placeRotation,
      smooth            = true
    })
  elseif (inDice.getRotationValue() == 6) then
    largeBag.takeObject(
    {
      position          = placePosition,
      rotation          = placeRotation,
      smooth            = true
    })
  end
end

function ClearAuction()
  --move any remaining Maoi back to their corresponding bag
  for i, maoi in ipairs(auctionScriptZ.getObjects()) do
    if (maoi.hasTag('small')) then
      smallBag.putObject(maoi)
    elseif(maoi.hasTag('medium')) then
      medBag.putObject(maoi)
    elseif(maoi.hasTag('large')) then
      largeBag.putObject(maoi)
    end
  end
end
